@End Reasoning
Process called "translate_constructor_declaration" takes ast as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Translate constructor declaration to HIR

    Let hir_constructor be proc create_hir_dict

    proc set_dict_value with hir_constructor, "node_type", "constructor_declaration"

    Let constructor_name be proc memory_get_int64 from Layout with ast, 16
    proc set_dict_value with hir_constructor, "name", constructor_name

    Note: Children mirror a method minus the return type: modifiers
    Note: (AST_MODIFIER_LIST), the parameter-list wrapper (AST_IDENTIFIER),
    Note: an optional throws type list, and the body (AST_BLOCK).
