End Process

@Reasoning:
Emits a type_parameter HIR dict with name and optional bounds. The first
child (if present) is the bound list — translate_type_bounds handles the
intersection form via repeated children.
@End Reasoning
Process called "translate_type_parameter" takes ast as Integer returns Integer:
